headline.main: Japan Says North Korean Missiles Landed as Close as 300 Km to Japan Coast
headline.print_headline: Japan Says North Korean Missiles Landed as Close as 300 Km to Japan Coast

lead_paragraph: Missiles fired by North Korea on Monday landed in waters as close as 300 km (186 miles) to Japan's northwest coast, Japan's Minister of Defence said.
